title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.30.08
description:
WERE THE CHILDREN BEATEN?:
    -------------------------
    Eight years ago, brothers Steven and Brandon were kidnapped by their father and were not heard from for five years. During that time, they claim they were physically and mentally abused. The boys&#039; father however, tells a much different tale, and he believes his angry ex-wife concocted their entire story. The deeper Steve digs into the story, the more he&#039;s finding something&#039;s not right, and he wants the truth!
